@startuml SystemContext
title 党员发展系统 - 角色与服务边界
left to right direction

actor "入党申请人" as Applicant
actor "党支部书记" as BranchSecretary
actor "组织员" as Organizer
actor "二级单位书记/副书记" as UnitLeader
actor "校党委组织部" as OrgDept
actor "超级管理员" as SuperAdmin

rectangle "客户端" {
  component "服务号 H5\n/wx-app/" as H5
  component "PC 后台" as PC
}

rectangle "Node API" {
  component "认证与权限守卫\nrequireAuth / requirePermission" as Auth
  component "数据范围守卫\nassertCanAccessApplicant" as Scope
  component "流程动作守卫\nassertWorkflowActor" as Actor
  component "流程服务\n前 12 步 MVP" as Workflow
  component "通知服务" as Notify
  component "统计与导出" as Export
}

database "MySQL" as DB
folder "uploads 文件目录" as Files

Applicant --> H5
BranchSecretary --> H5
Organizer --> H5
BranchSecretary --> PC
Organizer --> PC
UnitLeader --> PC
OrgDept --> PC
SuperAdmin --> PC

H5 --> Auth
PC --> Auth
Auth --> Scope
Scope --> Actor
Actor --> Workflow
Workflow --> DB
Workflow --> Files
Workflow --> Notify
Notify --> DB
PC --> Export
Export --> DB
@enduml

@startuml RegistrationApprovalSequence
title 注册审批时序
autonumber
actor "入党申请人/管理角色" as Applicant
participant "服务号 H5" as H5
participant "Node API" as API
participant "认证/权限守卫" as Auth
database "MySQL" as DB
actor "组织员/管理员" as Organizer

Applicant -> H5: 首次注册(name/idNo/employeeNo/password)
H5 -> API: POST /api/auth/register
API -> DB: 查询预置 users.username = employeeNo
alt 预置人员不存在
  API --> H5: 400 后台未找到预置人员信息
else 预置人员存在
  API -> DB: 写 registration_requests(pending)
  API -> DB: 记录审计日志
  API --> H5: 已提交，等待审核
end

Organizer -> API: POST /api/auth/approve-registration
API -> Auth: requireAuth + requirePermission(approve_registration)
Auth --> API: 已登录且有审批权限
API -> DB: 读取注册申请和目标用户范围字段
API -> Auth: canAccessScopedRecord(审批人, 申请人)
alt 无权限或跨范围
  API --> Organizer: 403
else pending 且范围覆盖
  API -> DB: 更新申请 status=approved/rejected
  opt approved
    API -> DB: 激活 users.status=active
    API -> DB: 确保 applicant 角色
  end
  API -> DB: 记录 approve_registration 审计
  API --> Organizer: 审批完成
end
@enduml

@startuml WorkflowReviewSequence
title 流程提交与审核时序
autonumber
actor "入党申请人" as Applicant
participant "H5/PC" as Client
participant "Node API" as API
participant "数据范围守卫" as Scope
participant "流程动作守卫" as Actor
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "通知服务" as Notify
actor "组织员/支部书记/责任角色" as Reviewer

Applicant -> Client: 填写步骤表单并提交
Client -> API: POST /api/*/workflows/:id/tasks|steps/:step/submit
API -> Scope: assertCanAccessApplicant(user, applicantId)
Scope --> API: 本人或管理范围内
API -> DB: getWorkflowByApplicantId(applicantId)
API -> Actor: assertWorkflowActor(submit)
Actor --> API: MVP节点 + 上一步已完成 + 申请人动作人
opt STEP_01
  API -> DB: 读取身份证号并校验年满18周岁
end
API -> DB: 更新 status=reviewing, task_status=in_review
API -> DB: 写 audit_logs
API -> Notify: notificationRecipientsForStep(step, applicantId)
Notify -> DB: 按责任角色和 org/branch 范围筛选收件人
Notify -> DB: 写 notifications
API --> Client: 任务已提交

Reviewer -> Client: 审核待办
Client -> API: POST /api/*/workflows/:id/tasks|steps/:step/review
API -> Scope: assertCanAccessApplicant(reviewer, applicantId)
API -> DB: getWorkflowByApplicantId(applicantId)
API -> Actor: assertWorkflowActor(review)
Actor --> API: 责任角色 + 当前节点可审核
alt approved
  API -> DB: 当前节点 approved/done/confirmed_at
  API -> DB: advanceAfterReview 打开下一 MVP 节点
  API -> Notify: 通知申请人已通过
else rejected
  API -> DB: 当前节点 rejected/blocked
  API -> DB: 锁定后续未完成 MVP 节点
  API -> Notify: 通知申请人补充材料
end
API --> Client: 审核结果已保存
@enduml

@startuml UploadSequence
title 材料上传时序
autonumber
actor "入党申请人" as Applicant
participant "服务号 H5" as H5
participant "Node API" as API
participant "数据范围守卫" as Scope
participant "流程动作守卫" as Actor
folder "uploads" as Files
database "MySQL" as DB

Applicant -> H5: 选择材料文件并上传
H5 -> API: POST /api/mobile/files/upload multipart(file, workflowId, stepCode, materialTag)
API -> API: validateUploadedFile(file, ['pdf','image'])
API -> Scope: resolve workflowId + assertCanAccessApplicant
Scope --> API: 本人或管理范围内
API -> DB: 读取 workflow + step
API -> Actor: assertWorkflowActor(submit)
API -> API: acceptedTypesForMaterial(step, materialTag)
API -> API: validateUploadedFile(file, material.accept)
alt 非法标签/空文件/类型不匹配/越权
  API --> H5: 400/403
else 校验通过
  API -> Files: multer 已保存临时文件
  API -> DB: 写 attachments
  API --> H5: attachmentId + fileUrl
end
@enduml

@startuml NotificationSequence
title 消息通知收件人筛选时序
autonumber
participant "流程服务" as Workflow
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "角色范围匹配" as Scope
actor "责任角色" as Reviewer
actor "申请人" as Applicant

Workflow -> DB: 读取 step.responsibleRoles
Workflow -> DB: 查询拥有责任角色的用户
loop 每个候选人
  Workflow -> Scope: roleMatchesApplicantScope(candidate, applicant)
  alt 范围覆盖且未被排除
    Scope --> Workflow: 保留为收件人
  else 范围不覆盖
    Scope --> Workflow: 丢弃
  end
end
Workflow -> DB: 写 notifications
Reviewer -> DB: H5/PC 拉取消息或待办
Applicant -> DB: H5 拉取审核结果通知
@enduml
